title: 12/25: 2020 Thoughts, Week 17 Tough Calls, Mailbag (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Merry Christmas! We're here to spread holiday cheer by looking back at 2019 lessons learned (3:05), looking ahead to 2020 breakouts (9:25) and talking about Week 17 ... News and notes (12:20) with updates on which teams are resting their starters. Then we've got Week 17 tough calls at QB (18:25), RB (25:05) and WR (31:40). How are we feeling about Matt Ryan, Tom Brady, Leonard Fournette, Deebo Samuel and Tyler Lockett, among others, this week? ... Answering your questions for 2020 and Week 17 ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
